Interface Orderable

DescSimulationObject
public interface Orderable
extends java.lang.Comparable

An "Orderable" object has a key which can be used to compare this object with other "Orderable" objects. The key must be a Comparable object.

The compareTo method of the classes that implements this interface should compare the keys of both objects.
